headline.main: Turkey Accuses Germany of 'Nazi' Practices; Rift Deepens
headline.print_headline: Turkey Accuses Germany of 'Nazi' Practices; Rift Deepens

lead_paragraph: A diplomatic rift between Turkey and key European nations deepened Sunday as President Recep Tayyip Erdogan accused Germany of "Nazi practices," days after a local authority prevented a Turkish minister from addressing a rally.
